1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 3]

2
00:00:16,100 --> 00:00:16,579
[Three days later]

3
00:00:16,660 --> 00:00:18,579
Nanxi, put away this wedding gown.

4
00:00:20,300 --> 00:00:21,379
I never expected you

5
00:00:21,540 --> 00:00:22,299
to have your own insights

6
00:00:22,580 --> 00:00:23,659
on dressing.

7
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:25,539
truly admire that.

8
00:00:31,260 --> 00:00:32,419
If you like them,

9
00:00:32,420 --> 00:00:33,819
I can give you some.

10
00:00:33,980 --> 00:00:35,499
They're not worth much.

11
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:36,579
Take them.

12
00:00:40,300 --> 00:00:41,299
I hope it's to your liking.

13
00:00:42,260 --> 00:00:43,299
Of course.

14
00:00:43,700 --> 00:00:44,739
I absolutely love them.

15
00:00:44,820 --> 00:00:45,979
Thank you, Fifth Concubine.

16
00:00:46,100 --> 00:00:47,299
If anything happens in the mansion,

17
00:00:47,380 --> 00:00:48,459
feel free to ask me.

18
00:01:00,420 --> 00:01:01,059
Smell this.

19
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:02,859
The sleeves seem to have a strange odor.

20
00:01:03,740 --> 00:01:05,219
It's the fragrance of plants.

21
00:01:08,140 --> 00:01:08,859
On the wedding day,

22
00:01:09,260 --> 00:01:10,739
the bats attacked only me and the lanterns.

23
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:16,899
Where were the taken-down lanterns stored?

24
00:01:17,220 --> 00:01:18,379
All in the storage room.

25
00:01:21,580 --> 00:01:22,419
Don't tell anyone about

26
00:01:22,980 --> 00:01:24,098
what we talked about today.

27
00:01:24,580 --> 00:01:25,098
Alright.

28
00:01:25,260 --> 00:01:26,259
I won't say a word.

29
00:01:26,500 --> 00:01:27,459
I'll take my leave now.

30
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:43,299
Exactly the same smell as on the wedding gown.

31
00:01:44,540 --> 00:01:46,339
So someone did tamper with it secretly.

32
00:01:46,540 --> 00:01:47,219
Steward,

33
00:01:47,540 --> 00:01:48,299
patrol the mansion more

34
00:01:48,300 --> 00:01:49,299
for the next few days.

35
00:01:49,460 --> 00:01:50,379
I'll handle the storage room.

36
00:01:50,460 --> 00:01:51,259
Yes, Second Young Master.

37
00:01:51,540 --> 00:01:52,539
Thank you for your trouble.

38
00:01:58,420 --> 00:01:59,859
Just as I thought. He showed up.

39
00:02:14,660 --> 00:02:15,659
What are you doing?

40
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:29,739
Second Young Master!
- Concubine!

41
00:02:29,740 --> 00:02:30,699
Save me!

42
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:36,139
Here you are, brother.

43
00:02:36,740 --> 00:02:37,579
Zhou Yimo,

44
00:02:38,580 --> 00:02:39,979
have you gone mad?

45
00:02:40,260 --> 00:02:41,499
Molesting the fifth concubine here?

46
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:47,179
Then

47
00:02:47,620 --> 00:02:48,939
I'll choose somewhere else next time.

48
00:02:50,380 --> 00:02:51,219
Young Master,

49
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:53,099
please don't force me

50
00:02:53,100 --> 00:02:54,459
to do things I don't want to do,

51
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:56,659
and stop helping Second Concubine

52
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:57,899
frame me.

53
00:03:02,100 --> 00:03:02,739
Let's go.

54
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:12,499
Please don't tell anyone about

55
00:03:13,740 --> 00:03:15,099
what just happened.

56
00:03:15,580 --> 00:03:16,259
Rest assured,

57
00:03:16,740 --> 00:03:18,019
I won't tell a soul.

58
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:21,539
Thank goodness you arrived in time.

59
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:24,019
Why did you ask me to

60
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:25,579
come to the storage room?

61
00:03:26,460 --> 00:03:27,499
I wanted to investigate

62
00:03:28,300 --> 00:03:30,099
the bat incident on the wedding day.

63
00:03:31,820 --> 00:03:33,339
I want to clear my name.

64
00:03:34,900 --> 00:03:36,259
Have you discovered anything?

65
00:03:36,380 --> 00:03:37,379
Do you remember

66
00:03:38,420 --> 00:03:39,339
that day

67
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:41,379
when bats flew into the wedding hall,

68
00:03:41,660 --> 00:03:42,379
but attacked only

69
00:03:42,380 --> 00:03:43,979
the master and me in our wedding gowns?

70
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:45,499
I remember.

71
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:47,019
Those bats

72
00:03:47,580 --> 00:03:49,179
also attacked the lanterns.

73
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:49,659
Right.

74
00:03:50,540 --> 00:03:51,579
I accidentally discovered

75
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:53,139
the wedding gown

76
00:03:53,660 --> 00:03:54,979
smells of bat grass.

77
00:03:56,660 --> 00:03:57,379
You mean

78
00:03:58,660 --> 00:03:59,939
someone wants to harm Father?

79
00:04:01,220 --> 00:04:03,859
So I went to check the storeroom

80
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:04,779
to try my luck

81
00:04:05,420 --> 00:04:06,219
and see if my deduction

82
00:04:06,620 --> 00:04:07,539
is correct.

83
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:10,059
Don't worry.

84
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,099
Leave this matter to me.

85
00:04:12,620 --> 00:04:13,939
I will clear your name.

86
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:19,819
Why do you believe me?

87
00:04:23,820 --> 00:04:24,739
You also believe me,

88
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:26,219
don't you?

89
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:38,819
Thank you, Second Young Master.

90
00:04:50,980 --> 00:04:53,659
It seems fifth concubine brings me luck.

91
00:04:54,180 --> 00:04:55,379
Congratulations, Master.

92
00:04:55,540 --> 00:04:56,179
Father.

93
00:04:56,900 --> 00:04:58,539
What's the rush?

94
00:04:58,540 --> 00:04:59,499
Forgive me, Father.

95
00:04:59,620 --> 00:05:00,659
I've lost my composure.

96
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:01,739
I found bat grass

97
00:05:02,220 --> 00:05:03,459
in your and Fifth Concubine's

98
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:05,459
wedding attire,

99
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:07,299
and in the wedding lanterns.

100
00:05:07,620 --> 00:05:08,579
Its scent

101
00:05:08,620 --> 00:05:09,779
attracts large numbers of bats.

102
00:05:10,620 --> 00:05:11,739
Someone wants to harm you, Father.

103
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:13,099
What?!

104
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:14,859
Investigate!

105
00:05:14,940 --> 00:05:16,099
Conduct a thorough investigation!

106
00:05:16,580 --> 00:05:17,699
Search the entire mansion

107
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:19,739
room by room.

108
00:05:19,900 --> 00:05:21,179
Search carefully!

109
00:05:21,740 --> 00:05:22,819
I want to see

110
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:25,299
who's trying to harm me behind my back.

111
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:27,979
Search!
- Yes!

112
00:05:33,420 --> 00:05:33,979
Steward.

113
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:35,219
Nothing.

114
00:05:35,820 --> 00:05:36,659
Understood.

115
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:38,419
Fifth Concubine.

116
00:05:39,180 --> 00:05:39,899
Excuse us.

117
00:05:49,780 --> 00:05:53,659
[Meng Wanzhi, third concubine]

118
00:05:57,140 --> 00:05:57,819
Third Concubine.

119
00:05:58,340 --> 00:05:59,059
Excuse us.

120
00:06:02,740 --> 00:06:03,619
Search everywhere!

121
00:06:03,620 --> 00:06:04,139
Yes!

122
00:06:04,140 --> 00:06:05,179
Why are you in my mother's room?

123
00:06:05,420 --> 00:06:05,899
Get out!

124
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:07,059
Father's orders.

125
00:06:07,740 --> 00:06:08,699
Zhou Yimo.

126
00:06:13,340 --> 00:06:14,419
That day in the storeroom,

127
00:06:14,820 --> 00:06:16,059
weren't you trying to destroy evidence

128
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:17,179
for Second Concubine?

129
00:06:21,740 --> 00:06:22,579
Zhou Yichen.

130
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:24,699
You need proof for such accusations.

131
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:27,299
Second Young Master,

132
00:06:27,540 --> 00:06:28,219
we found something.

133
00:06:43,620 --> 00:06:44,459
Speak!

134
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:46,939
What is this?

135
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:49,379
This is my medicine.

136
00:06:50,140 --> 00:06:51,379
As for its purpose

137
00:06:56,140 --> 00:06:57,659
I can't say in front of all these people.

138
00:06:57,700 --> 00:06:58,379
Speak!

139
00:06:59,980 --> 00:07:01,539
I really can't say it here.

140
00:07:01,540 --> 00:07:02,819
Just say it!

141
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:05,819
What did you buy this for?

142
00:07:05,980 --> 00:07:07,099
It's bat grass.

143
00:07:08,140 --> 00:07:10,219
I bought it to ease menstrual pain.

144
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:11,579
What's wrong, Master?

145
00:07:12,420 --> 00:07:13,259
Don't scare me.

146
00:07:13,620 --> 00:07:15,419
This grass was found

147
00:07:15,420 --> 00:07:16,139
in the lanterns

148
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:17,859
and also in her wedding gown and mine.

149
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:19,499
What is the meaning of this?

150
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:24,819
I don't know!

151
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:25,859
Master!

152
00:07:26,260 --> 00:07:27,899
Surely you don't suspect me

153
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:29,259
of sabotaging the wedding?

154
00:07:29,540 --> 00:07:30,539
What do you think?

155
00:07:30,780 --> 00:07:32,459
I've been having my period these past few days.

156
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:33,659
I feel so uncomfortable.

157
00:07:34,100 --> 00:07:35,899
These are the medicines the doctor just prescribed for me.

158
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:37,459
Then why did you

159
00:07:37,820 --> 00:07:39,939
drink several cups of herbal tea yesterday?

160
00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:42,579
Master,

161
00:07:43,100 --> 00:07:43,539
that's not it.

162
00:07:44,060 --> 00:07:45,339
It's because I've been suffering from

163
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:46,379
internal heat.

164
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:48,259
That's why I drank a few cups!

165
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:50,499
It must be you, Ye Zhiqiu, you bitch!

166
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:51,739
You knew I was using bat grass,

167
00:07:51,740 --> 00:07:52,899
so you framed me

168
00:07:52,900 --> 00:07:54,099
for all of this!

169
00:07:54,140 --> 00:07:55,419
The Fifth Concubine just entered the manor.

170
00:07:56,620 --> 00:07:57,379
Why would she

171
00:07:57,780 --> 00:07:59,699
frame you, Second Concubine?

172
00:07:59,740 --> 00:08:00,659
She envies me!

173
00:08:01,140 --> 00:08:02,259
She envies my noble background

174
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:03,739
and Master's favor towards me!

175
00:08:04,340 --> 00:08:05,299
She has plenty of reasons

176
00:08:05,300 --> 00:08:06,739
to frame and accuse me!

177
00:08:08,100 --> 00:08:09,379
Then why

178
00:08:09,460 --> 00:08:11,819
were you at the pond late at night?

179
00:08:12,420 --> 00:08:13,259
You often say

180
00:08:13,260 --> 00:08:14,579
you're afraid of the dark and timid.

181
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:16,539
So why would you

182
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:18,219
go there late at night?

183
00:08:19,740 --> 00:08:21,619
I was invited there by a letter.

184
00:08:22,620 --> 00:08:23,259
What letter?

185
00:08:24,180 --> 00:08:25,259
What does it invite you to do?

186
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:28,899
I...

187
00:08:32,140 --> 00:08:32,619
Speak!

188
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:33,499
Master,

189
00:08:33,940 --> 00:08:35,979
after all these years of marriage,

190
00:08:35,980 --> 00:08:37,379
you know me best.

191
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:39,579
You're the only man I've ever had.

192
00:08:39,780 --> 00:08:40,539
I would never

193
00:08:40,540 --> 00:08:41,939
betray you!

194
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:43,819
Wangshu,

195
00:08:44,980 --> 00:08:47,539
your usual rivalry in the inner courtyard

196
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:48,779
was tolerable.

197
00:08:49,460 --> 00:08:51,899
But now you know I took the Fifth Concubine

198
00:08:51,900 --> 00:08:52,979
to ward off evil spirits,

199
00:08:52,980 --> 00:08:54,619
yet you deliberately sabotaged it.

200
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:56,539
Do you want to kill me?

201
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:04,459
Ye Zhiqiu, you bitch!

202
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:26,059
How dare you hit me!

203
00:09:27,380 --> 00:09:28,419
Master, look at her!

204
00:09:32,060 --> 00:09:33,019
So what if I hit you?

205
00:09:34,460 --> 00:09:35,539
Do you think I'm one of those

206
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:37,219
timid maids around you?

207
00:09:37,220 --> 00:09:39,339
If you want to compete for favor, do it openly!

208
00:09:40,060 --> 00:09:41,499
What good does it do you

209
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:43,019
to harm both me and the Zhou family?

210
00:09:44,100 --> 00:09:44,699
Enough!

211
00:09:46,420 --> 00:09:47,179
Chen,

212
00:09:47,540 --> 00:09:49,179
send Second Concubine back to her room.

213
00:09:49,460 --> 00:09:50,739
I don't want to see her anymore...

214
00:09:55,180 --> 00:09:56,059
Master!

215
00:09:56,940 --> 00:09:58,579
I'm truly innocent!

216
00:09:59,580 --> 00:10:00,979
You don't believe me?

217
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:01,659
Second Concubine.

218
00:10:01,660 --> 00:10:02,699
And you actually believe her?

219
00:10:04,300 --> 00:10:05,059
After you.

220
00:11:00,740 --> 00:11:01,779
Sister...

221
00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:06,819
Sister...

222
00:11:07,580 --> 00:11:09,379
I've come for you.

223
00:11:14,980 --> 00:11:15,899
Sister?

224
00:11:22,660 --> 00:11:23,659
I don't want to die!

225
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:25,059
Don't take me away!

226
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:28,379
Then tell me one thing,

227
00:11:28,780 --> 00:11:30,099
and I'll let you go.

228
00:11:31,180 --> 00:11:32,819
Three years ago on New Year's Eve,

229
00:11:33,300 --> 00:11:34,539
how did you kill

230
00:11:34,540 --> 00:11:36,499
your personal maid Chuxue?

231
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:37,539
Speak!

232
00:11:41,820 --> 00:11:44,859
[On New Year's Eve three years ago]

233
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:58,339
Didn't you always want to save money

234
00:11:58,540 --> 00:12:00,179
for your sister's education?

235
00:12:01,340 --> 00:12:02,899
Just get through tonight,

236
00:12:03,340 --> 00:12:04,379
and I promise,

237
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:07,539
I'll support her until graduation.

238
00:12:10,900 --> 00:12:11,619
Second concubine!

239
00:12:11,780 --> 00:12:12,779
The Master said

240
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:15,379
no concubine may enter his room tonight.

241
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:16,179
Otherwise,

242
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:17,059
we'll be punished.

243
00:12:18,220 --> 00:12:18,859
Get out!

244
00:12:19,580 --> 00:12:20,379
Second concubine!

245
00:12:35,860 --> 00:12:37,459
That scarlet scarf you've been longing for

246
00:12:37,460 --> 00:12:39,219
I've finally knitted for you.

247
00:12:39,380 --> 00:12:39,979
Here,

248
00:12:40,580 --> 00:12:41,739
let me put it on you.

249
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:48,779
After New Year, I'm quitting school

250
00:12:49,900 --> 00:12:51,379
and taking a job

251
00:12:51,860 --> 00:12:54,219
as the Young Master's maid at Zhou Manor.

252
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:55,539
The pay is good.

253
00:12:56,580 --> 00:12:57,459
From now on,

254
00:12:58,740 --> 00:13:00,259
I'll fund your medical school education.

255
00:13:01,500 --> 00:13:02,139
No!

256
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:06,259
I won't let you be someone's slave!

257
00:13:09,660 --> 00:13:10,579
Silly goose,

258
00:13:12,860 --> 00:13:15,099
Sun Yat-sen Medical School is hard to get into,

259
00:13:15,820 --> 00:13:17,899
and you've only two years left till graduation.

260
00:13:18,540 --> 00:13:19,699
You must finish it.

261
00:13:21,740 --> 00:13:22,859
When you

262
00:13:23,300 --> 00:13:24,659
become a doctor,

263
00:13:25,540 --> 00:13:26,699
take me away with you.

264
00:13:28,100 --> 00:13:28,939
We'll

265
00:13:28,940 --> 00:13:30,819
make an honest living.

266
00:13:35,580 --> 00:13:36,179
Master,

267
00:13:36,660 --> 00:13:38,219
we've drawn enough blood.

268
00:13:38,580 --> 00:13:39,819
We'll transfuse you now.

269
00:13:40,260 --> 00:13:41,059
I guarantee

270
00:13:41,180 --> 00:13:41,859
within three days,

271
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:44,059
all your chronic ailments will vanish.

272
00:13:44,380 --> 00:13:45,499
and youth will be restored.

273
00:13:46,780 --> 00:13:47,339
Good!

274
00:13:47,860 --> 00:13:48,499
Excellent!

275
00:13:49,860 --> 00:13:50,499
Chuxue,

276
00:13:50,980 --> 00:13:52,379
if this treatment cures me,

277
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:54,539
I'll reward you handsomely.

278
00:13:57,340 --> 00:13:58,459
There's a box of tonics by the door.

279
00:13:58,980 --> 00:14:00,379
Take it to boost your health.

280
00:14:01,660 --> 00:14:02,699
Never mention this

281
00:14:03,260 --> 00:14:04,699
to anyone.

282
00:14:05,340 --> 00:14:06,019
Understood?

283
00:14:33,060 --> 00:14:34,579
How dare you seduce the Master!

284
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:40,619
These premium ginseng and lingzhi mushrooms

285
00:14:41,180 --> 00:14:42,819
are too good for a wretch like you!

286
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:56,539
How did you seduce the Master?

287
00:14:57,300 --> 00:14:58,099
Speak!

288
00:14:59,220 --> 00:15:00,299
I didn't!

289
00:15:01,620 --> 00:15:02,419
I didn't!

290
00:15:02,700 --> 00:15:03,819
I did nothing!

291
00:15:04,300 --> 00:15:06,139
If you dare steal him from me,

292
00:15:06,700 --> 00:15:08,539
I'll leave you with nothing!

293
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:29,619
I thought she seduced the Master,

294
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:30,819
so I punished her.

295
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:32,619
But I didn't kill her.

296
00:15:40,660 --> 00:15:43,579
Why can't the Master love only me?

297
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:46,139
First it was you,

298
00:15:46,420 --> 00:15:48,419
then Third concubine, Fourth concubine,

299
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:50,099
my personal maid,

300
00:15:50,460 --> 00:15:51,459
Fifth concubine...

301
00:15:54,300 --> 00:15:55,859
Why can't the Master see through

302
00:15:55,860 --> 00:15:57,899
their schemes?

303
00:16:01,460 --> 00:16:02,779
He loves no one

304
00:16:03,740 --> 00:16:04,939
but himself.

305
00:16:10,380 --> 00:16:11,419
Tell me,

306
00:16:13,860 --> 00:16:15,419
did I really do wrong?

307
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:17,219
You're dead wrong!

308
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:20,219
You've harmed innocent Chuxue.

309
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:25,539
Go!

310
00:16:26,260 --> 00:16:26,979
Get lost!

311
00:16:36,260 --> 00:16:36,939
Put me down!

312
00:16:37,300 --> 00:16:38,059
Don't move!

313
00:16:43,220 --> 00:16:44,059
What are you up to?
